ommons.law.umaryland.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1096&context=mscas|editor2-first=Chih-Yu|editor2-last=Wu|editor-first=Hungdah|editor-last=Chiu|last2=L. Wagner|last=L. Y. Yang|pages=279|location=Baltimore, Maryland|isbn=0-925153-07-9|year=1990|publisher=School of Law University of Maryland|first=Winston|chapter=TIANANMEN AND ITS IMPACT|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919085148/https://digitalcommons.law.umaryland.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1096&context=mscas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。格林纳达已于2005年恢复与中华人民共和国的外交关系。
